                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-409" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SELF</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 126.) I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> Did I not put it down at the door, and you said "Take it up again?" <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> You had put it down—I did not see you look at the things—the linen was hot and wet out of the copper or tub.</p>
               <p>(John Bradbury gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
